---
/* Luna's Procrasti-log: Final Edition */
---

<div class="procrasti-container">
    <section class="funkyyyy-card boots-section">
        <header class="card-header">
            <h2 class="glitch-text">BOOTSSCHULE LOG: 01:00 AM</h2>
            <span class="status-tag">SYSTEM: CRITICAL</span>
        </header>

        <div class="image-grid">
            <div class="img-wrapper">
                <img src="/PICS/mrspuff.jpg" alt="Mrs.Puff is going to the looney bin" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('fullscreen')" />
                <span class="caption">Mrs.Puff is going to the looney bin</span>
            </div>
            <div class="img-wrapper">
                <img src="/PICS/kms.jpg" alt="jk haha unless" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('fullscreen')" />
                <span class="caption">jk haha unless</span>
            </div>
            <div class="img-wrapper">
                <img src="/PICS/ithatesluna.png" alt="fml" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('fullscreen')" />
                <span class="caption">fml</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="rant-list">
            <li>We can do anything if we just believe in ourselves (delusional).</li>
            <li>Setup is a nightmare and we hate SQL. Luna vs. Campus Cloud is the beef of the century.</li>
            <li>Preliminary projects are a trap. Avoid at all costs.</li>
            <li>Sorry about the 40GB node_modules upload. We are idiots, but we are learning.</li>
            <li>Coordinating group coding is basically a psychological experiment.</li>
            <li>Autodeploy is a weapon of mass frustration.</li>
            <li><strong>BEST-FRIENDSHIP WITH CAMPUS CLOUD ENDED.</strong></li>
            <li>Wishing for a console is a daily ritual.</li>
            <li>Hätte früher mein Gehööörn benutzen sollen.</li>
            <li>Please tell me I deleted the Copilot Desperate .mds. Please.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="funkyyyy-card philosophy-section">
        <header class="card-header">
            <h2>THE BARE-MINIMUM</h2>
            <span class="status-tag accent">PROTOCOL: SURVIVAL</span>
        </header>

        <div class="grid-layout">
            <div class="steps-column">
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li>Wake the fuck up, Samurai. We have a city to burn.</li>
                    <li>Pick <strong>ONE</strong> task. Just one. Don't be a hero.</li>
                    <li>Cut it down until it’s as small as your will to live.</li>
                    <li>30-minute timer. Then leave. Literally go away.</li>
                    <li>You actually like this shit. Just <em>Shia LeBauf</em> "DO IT!"</li>
                    <li>Reward yourself like a toddler: snack, sticker, cigarette.</li>
                    <li>You got this, sweetie (unironically).</li>
                    <li>Rinse, reboot, repeat.</li>
                    <li>Bro, is that peanut butter? And a giant spoon? Valid.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="manifesto-column">
                <div class="manifesto-box">
                    <p>
                        <strong>PHILOSOPHY:</strong> Motivation is a scam, and discipline is shame wearing a suit.
                        Capitalism thrives on you being tired and scared. If you’re exhausted, the machine is working.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Your brain isn’t broken, the system is. Go check out <strong>Andrea Wu's Website</strong> to join the fight.
                    </p>
                    <p class="call-to-action">
                        The gods allowed you to live another day. <br/>
                        <strong>MAKE IT EVERYBODY ELSE'S PROBLEM.</strong>
                    </p>
                    <p class="fine-print">
                        Tiny steps count. Bare minimum counts. “I showed up” counts.
                        If you crash, you didn’t fail. Drink water. Breathe. Steal your life back one minute at a time.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    /* Using your global variables */
    .procrasti-container {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Figtree', sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    .funkyyyy-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .card-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        font-weight: 900;
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text);
    }

    .status-tag {
        background: var(--border);
        padding: 4px 12px;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .status-tag.accent {
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
    }

    /* IMAGE GRID & LIGHTBOX */
    .image-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .img-wrapper {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 10px;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        cursor: zoom-in;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .img-wrapper img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: grayscale(0.8);
        transition: filter 0.3s ease;
    }

    .img-wrapper:hover img {
        filter: grayscale(0);
    }

    /* FULLSCREEN CLASS (Lightbox) */
    .img-wrapper.fullscreen {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        z-index: 9999;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
        cursor: zoom-out;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 40px;
    }

    .img-wrapper.fullscreen img {
        width: auto;
        max-width: 90%;
        height: auto;
        max-height: 80vh;
        filter: grayscale(0);
        box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,1);
    }

    .img-wrapper.fullscreen .caption {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .caption {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-top: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* LISTS */
    .rant-list, .step-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .rant-list li::before {
        content: ">> ";
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .rant-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .step-list {
        counter-reset: step-counter;
    }

    .step-list li {
        counter-increment: step-counter;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        padding-left: 3.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .step-list li::before {
        content: counter(step-counter);
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: -2px;
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        width: 2.2rem;
        height: 2.2rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: 900;
        transform: rotate(-5deg);
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* MANIFESTO */
    .grid-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .grid-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    .manifesto-box {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        border: 1px dashed var(--primary);
        padding: 2rem;
        height: fit-content;
    }

    .manifesto-box p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .call-to-action {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 900;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 1.2rem !important;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
        padding-left: 15px;
    }

    .fine-print {
        font-size: 0.8rem !important;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .glitch-text:hover {
        animation: glitch 0.3s infinite;
        color: var(--primary);
    }

    @keyframes glitch {
        0% { transform: translate(0) }
        20% { transform: translate(-2px, 2px) }
        40% { transform: translate(-2px, -2px) }
        60% { transform: translate(2px, 2px) }
        80% { transform: translate(2px, -2px) }
        100% { transform: translate(0) }
    }
</style>